<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    #set($version="20170904")
    #set($src="http://f.51fanbei.com/h5/app/activity/09")
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>校园生活</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dist/activity/08/schoolLife.css">
</head>
<body>
<div id="schoolLife">
    <div class="banner"><img :src="content.bannerUrl"></div>
    <div class="couponList clearFix">
        <div class="coupon" v-for="item in couponCont.couponInfoList" @click="couponClick(item)">
            <p class="couponMoney">{{item.amount}}</p>
            <p class="couponRule" v-if="item.limitAmount>0">（满{{item.limitAmount}}元使用）</p>
            <p class="couponRule" v-else>无门槛</p>
            <p class="buyNow" v-if="item.drawStatus==='N'">立即领取</p>
            <p class="buyNow" v-if="item.drawStatus==='Y'">已领取</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="firstCont clearFix">
        <div class="contTitle">
            <p class="titleName">买部新手机 记录新的征程</p>
            <p class="titleDes">从家到学校的轨迹是成长离家求学的酸甜苦辣，对家人的思念用新手机让爱时刻连线遇见不同的人，经历不一样的精彩用新手机记录下来</p>
        </div>
        <div class="good" v-for="item in content.oneLevelGoodsInfo.goodsList" @click="goodClick(item)">
            <p class="goodImg"><img class="lazy" :data-original="item.goodsIcon"></p>
            <p class="goodDes">{{txtFix(item.goodName,8)}}</p>
            <p class="goodPrice clearFix"><span class="originPrice">￥{{item.saleAmount}}</span><span class="fan"></span><span class="fanMoney">￥{{item.rebateAmount}}</span></p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='1'|| item.nperMap.isFree==='2'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.freeAmount}}起</p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='0'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.amount}}起</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="firstCont secondCont clearFix">
        <div class="contTitle">
            <p class="titleName">宿舍篇</p>
            <p class="titleDes">没有新颖亮丽的墙面，却止不住的激动羞涩地与室友张罗布置这个叫宿舍的地方，是我们以后四年的家</p>
        </div>
        <div class="good" v-for="item in content.twoLevelGoodsInfo.goodsList" @click="goodClick(item)">
            <p class="goodImg"><img class="lazy" :data-original="item.goodsIcon"></p>
            <p class="goodDes">{{txtFix(item.goodName,8)}}</p>
            <p class="goodPrice clearFix"><span class="originPrice">￥{{item.saleAmount}}</span><span class="fan"></span><span class="fanMoney">￥{{item.rebateAmount}}</span></p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='1'|| item.nperMap.isFree==='2'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.freeAmount}}起</p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='0'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.amount}}起</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="firstCont thirdCont clearFix">
        <div class="contTitle">
            <p class="titleName">校园篇</p>
            <p class="titleDes">穿着轻装，轻踩单车、轻吹口哨在青春校园里，怀揣不知名的微微悸动展开一场名为探索的小旅行</p>
        </div>
        <div class="good" v-for="item in content.threeLevelGoodsInfo.goodsList" @click="goodClick(item)">
            <p class="goodImg"><img class="lazy" :data-original="item.goodsIcon"></p>
            <p class="goodDes">{{txtFix(item.goodName,8)}}</p>
            <p class="goodPrice clearFix"><span class="originPrice">￥{{item.saleAmount}}</span><span class="fan"></span><span class="fanMoney">￥{{item.rebateAmount}}</span></p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='1'|| item.nperMap.isFree==='2'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.freeAmount}}起</p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='0'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.amount}}起</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="firstCont fourthCont clearFix">
        <div class="contTitle">
            <p class="titleName">操场篇</p>
            <p class="titleDes">尖锐哨响，伴随着篮球拍击地面的砰砰声烧红的地面，一遍又一遍的冲刺之后原来，汗水的味道就是青春的味道</p>
        </div>
        <div class="good" v-for="item in content.fourLevelGoodsInfo.goodsList" @click="goodClick(item)">
            <p class="goodImg"><img class="lazy" :data-original="item.goodsIcon"></p>
            <p class="goodDes">{{txtFix(item.goodName,8)}}</p>
            <p class="goodPrice clearFix"><span class="originPrice">￥{{item.saleAmount}}</span><span class="fan"></span><span class="fanMoney">￥{{item.rebateAmount}}</span></p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='1'|| item.nperMap.isFree==='2'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.freeAmount}}起</p>
            <p class="monthPrice" v-if="item.nperMap.isFree==='0'">月供￥{{item.nperMap.amount}}起</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/dist/activity/08/schoolLife.js?version=$version"></script>
</body>
</html>